OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud affecting many in
OL,6,Fthe morning, clear for others. A
OL,7,Fbright and sunny afternoon to follow
OL,8,Ffor most. Breezy, especially along the
OL,9,Fcoast. Feeling hot for many inland, a
OL,10,Fslightly cooler feel by the sea.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA clear evening for many.
OL,13,FSome cloud makes progress inland, but
OL,14,Fit will remain clear along the south
OL,15,Fcoast. A light to gentle northeasterly
OL,16,Fbreeze, staying windier along the
OL,17,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
