OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FPatchy cloud soon clears to
OL,6,Fgive a bright and sunny day. Sunshine
OL,7,Fperhaps turning a little hazy by the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Remaining breezy along the
OL,9,Fcoast with a brisk northeasterly wind.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSettled
OL,12,Fwith sunny spells. Feeling cooler by
OL,13,Fthe weekend than in previous days with
OL,14,Fa northerly breeze, though daytime
OL,15,Ftemperatures likely remaining slightly
OL,16,Fabove average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
